		<item>
		<title>20 Powerful PHP Scripts for Adding Extra Functionality to Your Site</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/TheRiverCurrent/~3/2Q4wc2Cv_4U/</link>
		<comments>http://marketblog.envato.com/resources/20-powerful-php-scripts-for-adding-extra-functionality-to-your-site/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2015 12:07:06 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Sufyan bin Uzayr]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Resources]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://marketblog.envato.com/?p=39613</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[<p>We have collected some of the most useful PHP scripts that every web developer should have safely stored in their development toolbox.</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="http://marketblog.envato.com/resources/20-powerful-php-scripts-for-adding-extra-functionality-to-your-site/">20 Powerful PHP Scripts for Adding Extra Functionality to Your Site</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="http://marketblog.envato.com">Market Blog</a>.</p>
]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Readymade <a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/category/php-scripts">PHP Scripts</a> can be very useful for web developers, especially when you are looking to directly implement a particular functionality in your projects, and wish to save time by not having to meddle with or worry about the most basic of features, such as contact forms or a chat box.</p>
<p>In this post, I have put together some of the most useful PHP scripts that a web developer should surely take a look at. So without wasting any more time, let us check out these awesome scripts that make our lives as developers easier.</p>
<hr />
<h2><b>YouTube Music Engine</b></h2>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/youtube-music-engine/7490975">YouTube Music Engine</a> lets you create a music player of sorts &#8212; users can add tracks to a playlist, choose songs, and listen to the collection of their choice. It also adds support for lyrics engine, advertisement systems, comment systems such as Disqus, and so on.</p>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/youtube-music-engine/7490975"><img src="http://marketblog.envato.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/php_scripts_02.jpg" alt="YouTube Music Engine" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-38610" /></a></p>
<hr />
<h2><b>Droppy &#8212; Online File Sharing</b></h2>
<p>As the name suggests, <a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/droppy-online-file-sharing/10575317">Droppy &#8212; Online File Sharing</a> lets you share multiple files with users. It supports SMTP, is translation ready and can be used to secure files via passwords.</p>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/droppy-online-file-sharing/10575317"><img src="http://marketblog.envato.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/php_scripts_03.jpg" alt="Droppy -- Online File Sharing" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-38610" /></a></p>
<hr />
<h2><b>Layered Popups</b></h2>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/layered-popups/6027291">Layered Popups</a> lets you create multi-layered popup windows. You can create AJAX-based forms and even integrate the same with services such as Campaign Monitor and MailChimp.</p>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/layered-popups/6027291"><img src="http://marketblog.envato.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/php_scripts_04.jpg" alt="Layered Popups" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-38610" /></a></p>
<hr />
<h2><b>Contact Form Generator</b></h2>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/contact-form-generator-form-builder/1719810">Contact Form Generator</a> is a simple script that helps you create feedback forms or online surveys. The forms are fully responsive, and can be integrated with MailChimp and Aweber.</p>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/contact-form-generator-form-builder/1719810"><img src="http://marketblog.envato.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/php_scripts_05.jpg" alt="Contact Form Generator" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-38610" /></a></p>
<hr />
<h2><b>Social Meet Script</b></h2>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/social-meet-script/9953591">Social Meet Script</a> is a Tinder-style script that creates a social networking site with geolocation search, support for advertisements, and user profiles. It integrates well with PayPal, and also support Bootstrap templates. Plus, it is backwards-compatible with several browsers, including IE 6!</p>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/social-meet-script/9953591"><img src="http://marketblog.envato.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/php_scripts_06.jpg" alt="Social Meet Script" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-38610" /></a></p>
<hr />
<h2><b>Simple Invoice Manager &#8212; Invoicing Made Easy</b></h2>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/simple-invoice-manager-invoicing-made-easy/4259689">Simple Invoice Manager &#8212; Invoicing Made Easy</a> is a PHP script to manage your invoices, payments, quotations and other client related information. It supports Bootstrap, is responsive, and even integrates with popular payment solutions such as PayPal and Skrill.</p>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/simple-invoice-manager-invoicing-made-easy/4259689"><img src="http://marketblog.envato.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/php_scripts_07.jpg" alt="Simple Invoice Manager -- Invoicing Made Easy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-38610" /></a></p>
<hr />
<h2><b>Premium URL Shortener</b></h2>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/premium-url-shortener/3688135">Premium URL Shortener</a> is a handy solution to shorten URLs, implement URL bookmarks, etc. It features a responsive layout based on Bootstrap, and offers seamless social<br />
networking integration and is backed by separate jQuery and    <a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/premium-url-shortener-wordpress-plugin/6726829">WordPress</a> plugins as well.</p>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/premium-url-shortener/3688135"><img src="http://marketblog.envato.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/php_scripts_08.jpg" alt="Premium URL Shortener" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-38610" /></a></p>
<hr />
<h2><b>Facebook Multi-Page &amp; Group Poster</b></h2>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/facebook-multipagegroup-poster/8496644">Facebook Multi-Page &amp; Group Poster</a> lets you publish content to Facebook pages and groups. If you are managing multiple Facebook pages and groups for your business or personal use, you can use this script to post content such as statuses, images, videos, quotes, and virtually everything else that Facebook allows.</p>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/facebook-multipagegroup-poster/8496644"><img src="http://marketblog.envato.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/php_scripts_09.jpg" alt="Facebook Multi-Page &amp; Group Poster" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-38610" /></a></p>
<hr />
<h2><b>Dynamic Website Compressor</b></h2>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/dynamic-website-compressor/2838376">Dynamic Website Compressor</a> lets you minify HTML, CSS and JS on the fly. You can easily minimize the size of your overall code, and this can help boost the performance of the overall web page in terms of speed. This script requires no coding skills and is fully compatible with CMSs such as WordPress, Joomla! and Magento.</p>
<hr />
<h2><b>Freelance Cockpit 2 &#8212; Project Management</b></h2>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/freelance-cockpit-2-project-management/4203727">Freelance Cockpit 2 &#8212; Project Management</a> is built to help freelancers manage their projects. It lets you keep track of support tickets, client details, invoices and recurring billing, etc. It integrates well with PayPal, supports Bootstrap templates and is fully responsive and translation ready.</p>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/freelance-cockpit-2-project-management/4203727"><img src="http://marketblog.envato.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/php_scripts_10.jpg" alt="Freelance Cockpit 2 -- Project Management" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-38610" /></a></p>
<hr />
<h2><b>PHP Flat Visual Chat</b></h2>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/php-flat-visual-chat/8641929">PHP Flat Visual Chat</a><br />
offers real time chat functionality that can be integrated with any PHP-powered website. It has a responsive design, and is also available in a    <a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/wp-flat-visual-chat/8329900">separate version for WordPress users</a>.</p>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/php-flat-visual-chat/8641929"><img src="http://marketblog.envato.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/php_scripts_11.jpg" alt="PHP Flat Visual Chat" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-38610" /></a></p>
<hr />
<h2><b>NewsMaker &#8212; CMS and Social Network</b></h2>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/newsmaker-cms-and-social-network/9788299">NewsMaker &#8212; CMS and Social Network</a> is a script to create a website with user-generated content. It features the functionality to upload and input content, including images, video and other media, as well as seamlessly share it across other social networks too. It can integrate with services such as Google Analytics and is fully responsive.</p>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/newsmaker-cms-and-social-network/9788299"><img src="http://marketblog.envato.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/php_scripts_12.jpg" alt="NewsMaker -- CMS and Social Network" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-38610" /></a></p>
<hr />
<h2><b>Android Push Notification Using GCM</b></h2>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/android-push-notification-using-gcm/10438688">Android Push Notification Using GCM</a> is a handy script that can send push notifications to Android users. If you coding for Android and need to handle server side requests in order to send push notifications via Google Cloud Services, but are unsure how to do the same, this PHP script is the solution you are looking for!</p>
<hr />
<h2><b>PHP Flat Estimation and Payment Forms</b></h2>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/php-flat-estimation-payment-forms/10550735">PHP Flat Estimation and Payment Forms</a><br />
lets you create simple and responsive cost estimates and payment forms. It works with virtually every PHP platform out there, but a    <a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/wp-flat-estimation-payment-forms-/7818230">separate version for WordPress users</a> is also available.</p>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/php-flat-estimation-payment-forms/10550735"><img src="http://marketblog.envato.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/php_scripts_14.jpg" alt="PHP Flat Estimation and Payment Forms" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-38610" /></a></p>
<hr />
<h2><b>Quform &#8212; Responsive AJAX Contact Form </b></h2>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/quform-responsive-ajax-contact-form/148273">Quform &#8212; Responsive AJAX Contact Form</a> is a feedback and contact form solution that can easily be embedded into any web page within minutes.</p>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/quform-responsive-ajax-contact-form/148273"><img src="http://marketblog.envato.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/php_scripts_15.jpg" alt="Quform -- Responsive AJAX Contact Form" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-38610" /></a></p>
<hr />
<h2><b>Auto Grid Responsive Gallery</b></h2>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/auto-grid-responsive-gallery/3864088">Auto Grid Responsive Gallery</a> seeks and locates images from the specified set of folders, and creates a responsive gallery using those images. It can automatically generate thumbnails, so you need not worry about anything else.</p>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/auto-grid-responsive-gallery/3864088"><img src="http://marketblog.envato.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/php_scripts_16.jpg" alt="Auto Grid Responsive Gallery" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-38610" /></a></p>
<hr />
<h2><b>User Login Register and User Management</b></h2>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/user-login-register-and-user-management/9617985">User Login Register and User Management</a> offers user registration, login and other management solutions.</p>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/user-login-register-and-user-management/9617985"><img src="http://marketblog.envato.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/php_scripts_17.jpg" alt="User Login Register and User Management" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-38610" /></a></p>
<hr />
<h2><b>Owl Chat &#8212; Responsive Chat Community</b></h2>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/owl-chat-responsive-chat-community/10546841">Owl Chat &#8212; Responsive Chat Community</a> is a responsive messaging script that offers support for embedded links, images and even YouTube videos. It also supports custom emojis and advertisements.</p>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/owl-chat-responsive-chat-community/10546841"><img src="http://marketblog.envato.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/php_scripts_18.jpg" alt="Owl Chat -- Responsive Chat Community" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-38610" /></a></p>
<hr />
<h2><b>Freelancer Office</b></h2>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/freelancer-office/8870728">Freelancer Office</a> is a PHP script for project management and productivity. It offers features such as a ticketing system, a planner, scheduling and task management, file manager, private messaging and invoices.</p>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/freelancer-office/8870728"><img src="http://marketblog.envato.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/php_scripts_19.jpg" alt="Freelancer Office" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-38610" /></a></p>
<hr />
<h2><b>Translate It</b></h2>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/translate-it/1270898">Translate It</a> is a free alternative to Google Translate API. It can automatically detect the current language and supports multiple languages.</p>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/translate-it/1270898"><img src="http://marketblog.envato.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/php_scripts_20.jpg" alt="Translate It" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-38610" /></a></p>
