		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://marketblog.envato.com/?p=39773</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[<p>Cloudrise is a stunning and gripping short animated movie set in a fantasy, almost steampunk world high above the clouds.</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="http://marketblog.envato.com/video-of-the-week/cloudrise-a-stunning-animated-short-about-lovers-and-sky-pirates/">Cloudrise &#8211; a Stunning Animated Short about Lovers and Sky Pirates</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="http://marketblog.envato.com">Market Blog</a>.</p>
]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Cloudrise is a stunning and gripping short animated movie set in a fantasy, almost steampunk world high above the clouds. The main characters are Miko and Tenku, two lovers that have to fight to survive as their airship, after an attack from sky pirates, begins to plunge dangerously from the sky.</p>
<p><iframe src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/119430601?color=d79ce6&#038;title=0&#038;byline=0&#038;portrait=0&#038;badge=0" width="660" height="371" frameborder="0" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe></p>
<p>The eight-minute minute short movie was created in only four months by Denver Jackson, a director with no previous animation or illustration experience. He just wanted to tell a &#8216;great story&#8217;. And a great story it is!</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="http://marketblog.envato.com/video-of-the-week/cloudrise-a-stunning-animated-short-about-lovers-and-sky-pirates/">Cloudrise &#8211; a Stunning Animated Short about Lovers and Sky Pirates</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="http://marketblog.envato.com">Market Blog</a>.</p>
