<hr />
<h4><b>Fenix</b> &#8211; Fullscreen Video &amp; Image Background<span style="float:right"><a rel="nofollow" class="btn btn--size-s"  target="_blank" href="http://themeforest.net/item/fenix-fullscreen-video-image-background/full_screen_preview/2063700">Preview</a></span></h4>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://themeforest.net/item/fenix-fullscreen-video-image-background/2063700">Fenix</a> is a creative portfolio WordPress theme with support for full-screen images and video.</p>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://themeforest.net/item/fenix-fullscreen-video-image-background/2063700"><img src="http://marketblog.envato.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/video_background_template_theme_11.jpg" alt="WordPress - Fenix - Fullscreen Video &amp; Image Background" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-38610" /></a></p>
